ike: ike (Internet Key exchange daemon and IPsec VPN client)
ike:
ike: It provides secure communications between hosts and VPN gateways.
ike: It offers many of the advanced features only found in expensive 
ike: commercial software solutions and provides compatibility for VPN 
ike: appliances produced by vendors such as Cisco, Juniper, Checkpoint, 
ike: Fortinet, Netgear, Linksys, Zywall and many others
ike: Written by Shrew Soft Inc under an open source licence
ike: 
ike: http://www.shrew.net/download/ike
ike: 
